**Untested edge cases:**
- In-memory `Map` is cleared on server restart (normal) but **never cleared between tests** — shared mutable state
- `x-forwarded-for` with proxy chain (`ip1, ip2, ip3`) — only `ip1` used, untested
- No IP when behind certain proxies (falls back to `'unknown'`) — all unknown-IP requests share one rate limit
- Test: `429` after 5 attempts, `200` after rate limit resets

